strings:
<voice_0x01001C8B><se_high>Princess Medea: I'm sorry.
Give me a minute...
<voice_0x01001C8C><se_high>Princess Medea: I spend my days thinking about what I should talk to you about the next time we come to the spring.

<voice_0x01001C8D><se_high>Princess Medea: But there are so many things to share.
Sometimes I just don't know where to start...
<voice_0x01001C8E><se_high>Princess Medea: Travelling together is so much fun, <hero>.
<voice_0x01001C8F><se_high>Princess Medea: But it would be even better if I weren't a horse.
